snippet.title: Jupiter Hell - Early Access Launch Trailer (Red Band)
snippet.description:
Available now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/811320/Jupiter_Hell/
Available now on GOG: https://www.gog.com/game/jupiter_hell 
Available now on Humble Store: https://www.humblebundle.com/store/jupiter-hell

Jupiter Hell is a turn-based shooter from the depths of cosmic hell, built on a classic roguelike framework updated with modern 3d graphics. Rip and tear zombies, demons and unmentionable monstrosities while stockpiling new weapons, abilities and equipment.

Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/jupiterhell
Jupiter Hell website: http://jupiterhell.com/
